title: Muska in Mexico by SUPRA Footwear
description: Inspired by Mexico’s ancient temples and the culture that created them, Muska designed a custom sculpture to reflect the city’s rich, artistic history while also representing skateboarding and the streets. After a brief test ride in a local park with Spencer Hamilton and Supra Mexico’s skate team, the sculpture, titled “El Sol, La Luna, Y Más Allá” was brought to the the store where it will reside permanently.
